snippet: A century-old time capsule, filled mostly with documents by long-gone Wall Street businessmen celebrating New York as a commercial hub, was unsealed Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Century-Old Time Capsule Unsealed in New York
headline.main: Century-Old Time Capsule Unsealed in New York

lead_paragraph: A century-old time capsule, filled mostly with documents by long-gone Wall Street businessmen celebrating New York as a commercial hub, was unsealed Wednesday.
